                Coccus <lb n="2"/>Annisi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXC <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Mesio <lb n="6"/>patri posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb von Z. 1 eine Scheibe (Rosette?) zwischen zwei Tieren; oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes männliche Büste. (B): Weber - Beutler-Kränzl - Selinger - Pesditschek: Z. 1: [C]occus.</p>
